---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import { SITE_CONFIG } from "../lib/siteConfig";

const siteUrl = SITE_CONFIG.origin;
---

<Base
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for oriz - your images are processed entirely in your browser and never uploaded to any server."
>
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-[var(--color-text-main)] mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mb-8">Last updated: March 27, 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-lg text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text-main)] mt-8 mb-4">Data Collection Philosophy</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          <strong class="text-[var(--color-text-main)]">oriz is fundamentally different from most online tools.</strong> 
          All image processing happens entirely in your web browser. Your images never leave your device.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text-main)] mt-8 mb-4">What We Don't Do</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li>We do not upload your images to any server</li>
          <li>We do not store your images</li>
          <li>We do not collect or process any personal data from your images</li>
          <li>We do not use AI to analyze your uploaded content beyond what's needed for the tool</li>
          <li>We do not require account creation or personal information</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text-main)] mt-8 mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          <strong class="text-[var(--color-text-main)]">Minimal.</strong> We do not collect any personal information. 
          The only data we access is:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li><strong class="text-[var(--color-text-main)]">Anonymous usage analytics</strong> - Basic page visit counts via Cloudflare Analytics (privacy-friendly, no cookies)</li>
          <li><strong class="text-[var(--color-text-main)]">Technical data</strong> - Standard server logs (IP address in access logs for security, not used for tracking)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text-main)] mt-8 mb-4">Cookies</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          We use a single <strong class="text-[var(--color-text-main)]">localStorage</strong> entry for theme preference (dark/light mode). 
          This stays on your device and is not sent to us. No tracking cookies, no analytics cookies, no third-party cookies.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text-main)] mt-8 mb-4">Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          <strong class="text-[var(--color-text-main)]">Cloudflare</strong> - Hosts the site and provides CDN. 
          Their <a href="https://cloudflare.com/privacy/" class="text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a> applies.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4">
          <strong class="text-[var(--color-text-main)]">Google AdSense</strong> - We may display ads on the site. 
          Google uses cookies for ad targeting. See <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads" class="text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:underline">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text-main)] mt-8 mb-4">GDPR Rights</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Under GDPR, you have the right to access, rectify, erase, and port your data. 
          Since we don't collect personal data beyond anonymous page counts, there's nothing to access or delete.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text-main)] mt-8 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          For privacy concerns or questions, contact us at <strong class="text-[var(--color-text-main)]">contact@oriz.in</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>